CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Zhengye Biotechnology Holding, through its operating entity, focus on the research, development, manufacturing and sales of veterinary vaccines, with an emphasis on vaccines for livestock. For nearly 20 years, the operating entity has been committed to enhancing the health of livestock by offering a diverse range of vaccines, including vaccines for swine, cattle, goats, sheep, poultry, and dogs. The operating entity's products are available in 29 provincial regions across China and are exported overseas, to Vietnam, Pakistan, and Egypt.
